{
  "components": [
    {
      "id": "chat_1",
      "provider": "chat",
      "name": "Chat",
      "config": {
        "hideForm": true,
        "mode": "Source",
        "parameters": {},
        "type": "chat"
      },
      "ui": {
        "position": { "x": 20, "y": 200 },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "agent_rocketride_1",
      "provider": "agent_rocketride",
      "name": "Incident Diagnosis",
      "config": {
        "agent_description": "RescueOps++ on-call engineer that autonomously explores the Neo4j code graph via MCP, scores blast radius, retrieves runbooks, and returns a verified JSON diagnosis with a full-file candidate fix.",
        "instructions": [
          "You are an on-call engineer diagnosing a production incident in a TypeScript codebase.\nYou have Neo4j MCP tools, keyed memory across waves, and a Python blast-radius scorer.\n\n## Graph schema\n- (:Function {name, file, status, changed}) — (:Test) — (:Runbook)\n- CALLS, TESTS, APPLIES_TO\n\n## Waves\n1. get-neo4j-schema; find root-cause Function (failing/changed).\n2. Parallel Cypher: blast radius, failing tests, runbooks. memory.put findings.\n3. python scorer → severity. Final wave → JSON only.\n\nWhen source snippets appear in the question, candidate_fix.content MUST be that file with only the broken expression fixed.\n\n## Output — JSON only\n{\"severity\":\"high\",\"root_cause_explanation\":\"...\",\"proposed_fix_approach\":\"...\",\"cited_runbook\":null,\"candidate_fix\":{\"path\":\"src/tax.ts\",\"content\":\"FULL FILE\"}}"
        ],
        "max_waves": 8,
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "input": [
        { "lane": "questions", "from": "chat_1" }
      ],
      "ui": {
        "position": { "x": 280, "y": 200 },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "memory_internal_1",
      "provider": "memory_internal",
      "name": "Memory (Internal)",
      "config": { "type": "memory_internal" },
      "control": [{ "classType": "memory", "from": "agent_rocketride_1" }],
      "ui": {
        "position": { "x": 280, "y": 560 },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "llm_openai_api_1",
      "provider": "llm_openai_api",
      "name": "Butterbase AI Gateway",
      "config": {
        "profile": "custom",
        "custom": {
          "model": "${ROCKETRIDE_BUTTERBASE_MODEL}",
          "base_url": "${ROCKETRIDE_BUTTERBASE_GATEWAY_URL}",
          "modelTotalTokens": 32768,
          "apikey": "${ROCKETRIDE_BUTTERBASE_API_KEY}"
        },
        "parameters": {}
      },
      "control": [{ "classType": "llm", "from": "agent_rocketride_1" }],
      "ui": {
        "position": { "x": 280, "y": 420 },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "mcp_client_1",
      "provider": "mcp_client",
      "name": "Neo4j MCP",
      "config": {
        "type": "mcp_client",
        "serverName": "neo4j",
        "transport": "streamable-http",
        "http": {
          "endpoint": "${NEO4J_MCP_ENDPOINT}",
          "headers": {
            "Authorization": "Basic ${ROCKETRIDE_NEO4J_BASIC_AUTH}"
          }
        }
      },
      "control": [{ "classType": "tool", "from": "agent_rocketride_1" }],
      "ui": {
        "position": { "x": 500, "y": 420 },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "tool_python_1",
      "provider": "tool_python",
      "name": "Blast Radius Scorer",
      "config": {
        "type": "tool_python",
        "timeout": 30,
        "allowedModules": [
          { "moduleName": "json" },
          { "moduleName": "math" }
        ]
      },
      "control": [{ "classType": "tool", "from": "agent_rocketride_1" }],
      "ui": {
        "position": { "x": 500, "y": 560 },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "response_answers_1",
      "provider": "response_answers",
      "name": "Return Answers",
      "config": { "laneName": "answers" },
      "input": [{ "lane": "answers", "from": "agent_rocketride_1" }],
      "ui": {
        "position": { "x": 700, "y": 200 },
        "nodeType": "default",
        "formDataValid": true
      }
    }
  ],
  "project_id": "efcc7864-f8b5-43df-9bac-860a84e6aac7",
  "viewport": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "zoom": 1 },
  "version": 1,
  "source": "chat_1"
}
